*Assessment*

While testing out the environment to confirm the fix for EUCA-13373, a cloudformation stack failed to deploy.  The following error was seen in the cloudformation events for the stack:
{code}
...
EVENT	DevOpsStack	84ceac71-2f94-42f5-8221-0b1a01dbfb46	AWS::CloudFormation::Stack	DevOpsStack	arn:aws:cloudformation::000317210923:stack/DevOpsStack/c86f14ea-58b9-4ef3-adcd-6c37e328fc48	2017-05-02T14:15:29.215Z	ROLLBACK_IN_PROGRESS	Create stack failed.  Rollback requested by user.
