EVENT	DevOpsStack	NginxELB-CREATE_FAILED-1493734512430	AWS::ElasticLoadBalancing::LoadBalancer	NginxELB		2017-05-02T14:15:12.430Z	CREATE_FAILED	Workflow for creating listeners has failed
